! Usages

!! Windows

use Git Bash:

```shell
$ sdk list java
$ sdk install 21.0.5-tem
$ sdk default java 17.0.9-tem

$ sdk install ant
$ sdk install maven
$ sdk install gradle
```

offline mode:

```shell
$ sdk offline enable
Offline mode enabled.

$ sdk list java
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Offline: only showing installed java versions
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 * 8.0.402-tem
 * 17.0.9-tem
 * 17.0.9-graalce
 * 11.0.22-tem
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* - installed
> - currently in use
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

$ sdk offline disable
Online mode re-enabled!
```



